headline: HP Stock Forecast: Can AI PCs and Windows 11 Refresh Take HPQ Higher?
summary: While HP stock has rebounded from its 2025 lows, it is still in the red for the year. The stock could rise further from these levels on AI PC sales and the Windows 11 refresh cycle.
